        <div class="PlayableMedia-externalUrlBlockContent">
          <div class="PlayableMedia-title">Our tax guarantee for the many </div>
          <div class="PlayableMedia-description">Our guarantee: No rise in Income Tax for 95% of taxpayers &amp; no rise in VAT or National Insurance for anyone. Only top 5% of earners will be asked to contribute more tax, to help fund public services.</div>
        </div>
  </div>
</div>

  </div>
</div>

          <p class="u-hiddenVisually" aria-hidden="true" data-aria-label-part="1">Steve Clapcote Retweeted Jeremy Corbyn</p>

  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="4">Labour will develop the economy of our region through fair and sustainable investment. <a href="/hashtag/VoteLabour?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>VoteLabour</b></a> <a href="/hashtag/Steve4Shipley?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>Steve4Shipley</b></a> <a href="/hashtag/Shipley?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>Shipley</b></a><a href="https://t.co/UzpzrP7IxB" rel="nofollow noopener" dir="ltr" data-expanded-url="https://twitter.com/jeremycorbyn/status/871652824689651712" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" target="_blank" title="https://twitter.com/jeremycorbyn/status/871652824689651712"><span class="tco-ellipsis"></span><span class="invisible">https://</span><span class="js-display-url">twitter.com/jeremycorbyn/s</span><span class="invisible">tatus/871652824689651712</span><span class="tco-ellipsis"><span class="invisible"></span></span></a></p>

</ul></div>
